high_descs: go to the desk that is in front of a book shelf with a computer on it
pick up the white coffee mug from the book shelf
go to the left end of the desk
place the mug on the left end of the desk
anns.task_desc: take a coffee mug from a book shelf and place it on a desk

high_descs: Turn to the right and then the left to the other side of the room, and face the desk on the left side. Look up to the books on the shelf.
Pick up the cup from the shelf.
Carry the cup and turn to the left and then face the desk on the right side.
Place the cup on the short side of the desk, close to you.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup from the shelf to the desk.

high_descs: Turn right at the brown desk and walk between the bed and the desk. Turn left at the orange cylinder on the right of the bed on the floor. Walk to the desk on your left with a laptop on it.
Pick up the white coffee mug that's on the desk.
Turn around and walk to the bed. Turn right at the bed.
Put the coffee mug back down on the left side of the desk to the right of the bed.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a coffee mug from the desk and put it down on the desk.
